    <header class="p-6 bg-black text-white flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">AstroPraxis</h1>
      <nav class="space-x-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:underline">About</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">AstroPraxis is powered by a diverse group of consultants, facilitators, and transformation strategists committed to equity, justice, and sustainable impact. For contact, reach us at <strong class="text-indigo-700">269.222.4330</strong>.</p>
